> JobConf access to name-values
> -----------------------------
>
>                 Key: HADOOP-345
>                 URL: http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-345
>             Project: Hadoop
>          Issue Type: Improvement
>            Reporter: Michel Tourn
