> the job tracker re-runs failed tasks on the same node
> -----------------------------------------------------
>
>                 Key: HADOOP-400
>                 URL: http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-400
>             Project: Hadoop
>          Issue Type: Bug
