> Safe mode and name node startup procedures
> ------------------------------------------
>
>                 Key: HADOOP-306
>                 URL: http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-306
>             Project: Hadoop
>          Issue Type: New Feature
>    Affects Versions: 0.3.2
