> RFC: Efficient file caching
> ---------------------------
>
>                 Key: HADOOP-288
>                 URL: http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-288
>             Project: Hadoop
>          Issue Type: Bug
>    Affects Versions: 0.6.0
>            Reporter: Michel Tourn
